n><pubDate>Tue, 17 Sep 2024 23:03:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/media-telecom/inside-us-push-steer-vietnams-subsea-cable-plans-away-china-2024-09-17/</guid></item><item><title>朝鲜一周内第二次发射短程弹道导弹</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/north-korea-appears-have-fired-ballistic-missile-japan-says-2024-09-17/</link><description>韩国和日本表示，朝鲜周三发射了多枚短程弹道导弹，落在其东海岸附近的海域，几天前平壤公布了一座铀浓缩设施，并誓言要加强其核武库。</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Sep 2024 22:03:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/north-korea-appears-have-fired-ballistic-missile-japan-says-2024-09-17/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：美联储千钧一发——等待即将结束</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-09-17/</link><description>展望未来一天的亚洲市场。</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Sep 2024 21:51:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-09-17/</guid></item><item><title>上半场进球帮助阿尔希拉尔取得亚洲冠军联赛首场胜利</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/first-half-goals-ease-al-hilal-opening-asian-champions-league-win-2024-09-17/</link><description>周二，沙特阿拉伯的阿尔希拉尔队以 3-1 战胜卡塔尔的阿尔雷扬队，豪尔赫·热苏斯的球队在艾哈迈德·本·阿里体育场举行的亚洲冠军联赛精英赛联赛阶段开局不利。</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Sep 2024 18:27:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/first-half-goals-ease-al-hilal-opening-asian-champions-league-win-2024-09-17/</guid></item><item><title>博世首席执行官认为全球汽车市场增长停滞</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/bosch-chief-sees-stagnating-growth-car-markets-worldwide-2024-09-17/</link><description>德国汽车供应商博世首席执行官史蒂芬·哈同（Stefan Hartung）在接受路透社采访时表示，预计今年和明年全球汽车和商用车市场增长幅度很小。</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Sep 2024 15:21:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/bosch-chief-sees-stagnating-growth-car-markets-worldwide-2024-09-17/</guid></item><item><title>中国保险经纪公司元宝在投资者兴趣复苏之际申请美国首次公开募股</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/chinese-insurance-broker-yuanbao-files-us-ipo-amid-reviving-investor-appetite-2024-09-17/</link><description>中国保险经纪公司元宝周二在美国申请首次公开募股，这表明投资者对新上市的兴趣全面复苏。</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Sep 2024 15:10:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/chinese-insurance-broker-yuanbao-files-us-ipo-amid-reviving-investor-appetite-2024-09-17/</guid></item><item><title>德拉吉表示，欧盟必须在与中国的清洁技术贸易上找到适当的平衡</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/eu-must-find-right-balance-clean-tech-trade-with-china-says-draghi-2024-09-17/</link><description>马里奥·德拉吉周二表示，依靠中国提供绿色产品可能是欧盟实现其气候雄心的最便宜途径，但欧盟需要对中国政府支持的竞争对手做出细致入微的反应，以保留自己的清洁技术工作岗位。</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Sep 2024 14:28:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/eu-must-find-right-balance-clean-tech-trade-with-china-says-draghi-2024-09-17/</guid></item><item><title>德国哈贝克呼吁政治解决与中国的电动汽车关税争端</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/germanys-habeck-calls-political-solution-ev-tariff-dispute-with-china-2024-09-17/</link><description>德国经济部长罗伯特·哈贝克周二在与中国商务部长王文涛会面后呼吁政治解决欧盟与中国之间关于电动汽车关税的争端。</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Sep 2024 13:58:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/germanys-habeck-calls-political-solution-ev-tariff-dispute-with-china-2024-09-17/</guid></item><item><title>中国联想将在印度生产人工智能服务器并开设新的以人工智能为中心的实验室</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/artificial-intelligence/chinas-lenovo-make-ai-servers-india-opens-new-ai-centric-lab-2024-09-17/</link><description>中国电子硬件制造商联想集团周二表示，该公司将开始在印度南部的工厂生产人工智能（AI）服务器，并在班加罗尔科技中心开设一个专注于人工智能服务器的研发实验室。</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Sep 2024 12:28:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/artificial-intelligence/chinas-lenovo-make-ai-servers-india-opens-new-ai-centric-lab-2024-09-17/</guid></item><item><title>早间出价：新高，美联储与零售健康检查进行轮换</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-pix-2024-09-17/</link><description>迈克·多兰 (Mike Dolan) 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Sep 2024 10:14:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-pix-2024-09-17/</guid></item><item><title>美国称海军飞机过境台湾海峡</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/us-says-navy-aeroplane-transits-taiwan-strait-2024-09-17/</link><description>周二，一架美国海军飞机飞越台湾海峡，美国称这是对自由开放国际空域的承诺，促使中国在其声称拥有的水道上紧急出动战斗机。</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Sep 2024 10:09:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/us-says-navy-aeroplane-transits-taiwan-strait-2024-09-17/</guid></item><item><title>美国对从中国进口的铀进行调查，以防止规避俄罗斯禁令</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/us-probes-uranium-jump-china-amid-concerns-over-russian-import-ban-2024-09-17/</link><description>任何规避行为都可能损害美国削减对俄罗斯资金的努力。这也损害了美国建立自己的铀供应链的尝试。</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Sep 2024 10:09:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/us-probes-uranium-jump-china-amid-concerns-over-russian-import-ban-2024-09-17/</guid></item></channel></rss>